%%{init: {'theme': 'default'}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Start: gforms diff] --> B[Load form definition]
    B --> C{Valid TypeScript?}
    C -->|No| D[Show validation errors]
    D --> E[Exit with error]

    C -->|Yes| F[Authenticate with Google]
    F --> G{Auth successful?}
    G -->|No| H[Show auth error]
    H --> E

    G -->|Yes| I[Check state file for form ID]
    I --> J{Form ID exists?}

    J -->|No| K[Form is NEW]
    K --> L[Show full form as additions]

    J -->|Yes| M[Fetch remote form]
    M --> N{Fetch successful?}
    N -->|No| O[Show network error]
    O --> E

    N -->|Yes| P[Compare local vs remote]
    P --> Q[Calculate question changes]
    Q --> R[Calculate integration changes]

    R --> S{Any changes?}
    S -->|No| T[No changes detected]
    T --> U[Exit code 0]

    S -->|Yes| V[Format diff output]
    L --> V

    V --> W{--ci flag?}
    W -->|Yes| X[Output machine-readable format]
    X --> Y[Exit code 1 - changes exist]

    W -->|No| Z[Output human-readable format]
    Z --> Y

    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style U fill:#c8e6c9
    style Y fill:#fff9c4
    style E fill:#ffcdd2
